553
00:47:13,890 --> 00:47:15,100
Vâng, thưa Chúa tể.

554
00:47:17,390 --> 00:47:18,720
Tôi xin lỗi!

555
00:47:18,770 --> 00:47:20,020
Ông là cái quái gì vậy?

556
00:47:20,060 --> 00:47:21,270
Tôi xin lỗi.

